text: The Cyprus Stock Exchange or CSE (, is an European stock exchange located in Cyprus. It was established under the Cyprus Securities Act. CSE was approved by the Chamber of Deputies in April 1993. Operations began on March 29, 1996. In 2006 a common platform was launched with the Athens Stock Exchange. CSE is a member of the Federation of Eurasian Exchanges. Category:Stock exchanges in Europe Category:Economy of Cyprus Category:1996 establishments in Europe Category:Organizations based in Cyprus
